26quot%3B%20Sembach%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20worked%20long%20hours%20with%20a%20ton%20of%20stress%20to%20ensure%20that%20my%20clients%20received%20not%20only%20adequate%20representation%2C%20but%20superb%20representation%2C%20because%20I%20knew%20that%20their%20lives%20were%20on%20the%20line%20and%20it%20was%20important%20to%20them.%20So%20it%20was%20important%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Sembach%20and%20Williams%20hold%206-figure%20student-loan%20balances%20from%20their%20educations.%20They're%20counting%20on%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20program%2C%20which%20relieves%20student%20debt%20for%20government%20and%20nonprofit%20workers%20after%2010%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20program%2C%20which%20started%20in%202007%2C%20has%20wiped%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-pslf-more-borrowers-approved-debt-cancellation-biden-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebillions%20of%20dollars%20in%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20but%20changes%20are%20looming.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20in%20March%20calling%20on%20the%20education%20secretary%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-limits-public-service-loan-forgiveness-program-pslf-education-department-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eredefine%20what%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20service%26quot%3B%20is%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20ensure%20that%20qualifying%20employers%20are%20not%20engaging%20in%20what%20the%20administration%20deems%20as%20%26quot%3Banti-American%26quot%3B%20activities%2C%20like%20discrimination%2C%20violations%20of%20federal%20immigration%20law%2C%20or%20services%20related%20to%20hormone%20changes%20or%20gender%20transitioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Education%20published%20its%20proposed%20rule%20on%20August%2018%20and%20acknowledged%20that%20some%20borrowers%20would%20not%20receive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-limits-pslf-student-loan-forgiveness-block-delay-debt-relief-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecredit%20toward%20forgiveness%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20their%20employer%20was%20ruled%20ineligible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20may%20delay%20or%20prevent%20forgiveness%20for%20a%20subset%20of%20borrowers%2C%20the%20overall%20design%20of%20the%20regulations%E2%80%94including%20advance%20notice%2C%20transparency%20around%20determinations%2C%20and%20employer%20recertification%20pathways%E2%80%94helps%20mitigate%20unexpected%20harm%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20rule%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20borrowers%20like%20Sembach%20and%20Williams%20are%20attempting%20to%20navigate%20repayment%20amid%20changes%20from%20the%20administration%2C%20with%20their%20sights%20set%20on%20loan%20forgiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20spoken%20with%20dozens%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%20grappling%20with%20changes%20to%20debt%20relief%20and%20repayment%20in%20the%20last%20year.%20Share%20your%20story%20by%20emailing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20read%20more%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-major-repayment-overhaul-big-beautiful-bill-trump-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHow%20Trump's%20big%20spending%20bill%20will%20overhaul%20repayment%20for%20millions%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-react-default-collections-wage-social-security-garnishment-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMillions%20of%20student-loan%20borrowers%20are%20about%20to%20be%20thrown%20into%20collections.%20Some%20say%20they're%20already%20'barely%20scraping%20by.'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-debt-retirement-default-collections-risk-social-security-checks-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStudent-loan%20debt%20followed%20them%20into%20retirement.%20Now%20it%20threatens%20their%20Social%20Security%20checks.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-limits-public-service-loan-forgiveness-borrowers-react-debt-relief-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EA%20new%20threat%20to%20public%20servants'%20key%20student-loan%20forgiveness%20has%20them%20on%20edge%3A%20'I'm%20so%20close%20to%20the%20finish%20line'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c7dc44d-0eef-4950-8e9b-40dedfecfac1%5C%22%3EA%20surge%20in%20student-loan%20payments%20and%20an%20interrupted%20timeline%20to%20relief%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%2C%2040%2C%20has%20%24127%2C000%20in%20student%20debt%20%E2%80%94%20which%20she%20started%20paying%20off%20in%202006%20%E2%80%94%20from%20her%20associate's%2C%20bachelor's%2C%20master's%2C%20and%20doctorate%20degrees.%20She's%20putting%20those%20degrees%20to%20use%20as%20a%20full-time%20nurse%20at%20a%20private%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20made%20payments%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20Williams%20should%20qualify%20for%20relief%20through%20PSLF.%20However%2C%20she%20was%20enrolled%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-student-loan-borrowers-cheaper-payments-debt-cancellation-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20been%20blocked%20since%20last%20summer%20due%20to%20legal%20challenges.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20her%20loans%20were%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eput%20on%20forbearance%2C%20and%20payments%20during%20that%20time%20did%20not%20qualify%20for%20PSLF%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20SAVE%2C%20her%20monthly%20bill%20spiked%20to%20%24925%20from%20%24155.%20She%20has%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20make%20that%20payment%2C%20hoping%20it'll%20get%20her%20back%20on%20track%20toward%20PSLF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20sell%20a%20kidney.%20I%20don't%20mind%20ramen%20noodles.%20I'm%20not%20financially%20at%20that%20point%20yet%2C%20but%20if%20it's%20four%20months%20of%20this%20payment%2C%20it's%20really%20going%20to%20start%20to%20hurt%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223392%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Malissa%20Williams%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a5b724cfc04e97619baf8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222544%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMalissa%20Williams%2C%20a%20nurse%2C%20is%20just%20four%20payments%20away%20from%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Malissa%20Williams%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Williams%20is%20navigating%20the%20PSLF%20buyback%20process%2C%20which%20allows%20borrowers%20who%20have%20made%20120%20qualifying%20payments%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20back%26quot%3B%20months%20spent%20in%20deferment%20or%20forbearance%20to%20earn%20PSLF%20credit.%20She%20needs%20to%20buy%20back%20four%20payments%20at%20her%20new%2C%20higher%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.dcd.278527%2Fgov.uscourts.dcd.278527.39.0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20court%20filing%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20said%20that%2C%20as%20of%20July%2031%2C%20there%20is%20a%2072%2C730-person%20backlog%20of%20buyback%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20nurse%20who%20worked%20through%20COVID%2C%20who%20didn't%20leave%20the%20bedside%20during%20COVID%2C%20and%20I'm%20struggling%20to%20even%20pay%20a%20student%20loan%20bill%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%2C%20including%20me%2C%20is%20just%20doing%20things%20to%20try%20to%20make%20these%20payments%20as%20quick%20as%20possible%20and%20just%20to%20get%20out%20of%20it%20before%20you%20can't%20get%20out%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292393d4d-bafb-4ccc-92c8-9f8c75eb7431%5C%22%3EHigh%20interest%20rates%20mean%20barely%20making%20a%20dent%20in%20a%206-figure%20balance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESembach%2C%20who%20previously%20served%20as%20a%20chief%20deputy%20public%20defender%20and%20now%20works%20for%20the%20Commonwealth%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20is%20set%20to%20receive%20PSLF%20relief%20on%20his%20%24263%2C000%20balance%20in%20September%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20never%20been%20opposed%20to%20paying%20off%20what%20he%20borrowed%3B%20the%20problem%2C%20he%20said%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20the%20high%20interest%20rate%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20make%20even%20a%20dent%20in%20his%20original%20balance.%20Interest%20rates%20on%20federal%20loans%20are%20fixed%20based%20on%20the%20year%20the%20loan%20was%20first%20taken%20out%2C%20and%20they%20are%20highest%20for%20graduate%20and%20professional%20student%20loans.%20Direct%20unsubsidized%20loans%20for%20that%20category%20now%20stand%20at%207.94%25%2C%20slightly%20above%20Sembach's%207.88%25%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20daunting%20and%20it%20almost%20feels%20like%20you're%20swimming%20against%20the%20current%2C%20but%20the%20current%20is%20incredibly%20strong%20because%20you%20know%20that%20what%20you're%20paying%20in%20isn't%20making%20a%20bit%20of%20difference%20and%20that%20the%20money%20continues%20to%20accrue%20against%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Sembach%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20also%20very%20disheartening.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Matt%20Sembach%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a5c2fba17a8c5b40532533%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221891%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESembach%20said%20high%20interest%20rates%20on%20student%20loans%20make%20repayment%20