ans%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%2C%20InMarket%20found.%20This%20rating%20was%20based%20on%20the%20chain's%20%26quot%3Bfidelity%20index%26quot%3B%20of%20327%2C%20a%20score%20determined%20by%20the%20ratio%20of%20guest%20visits%20to%20a%20location%20compared%20to%20the%20number%20of%20the%20chain's%20locations%20nationwide.%20A%20score%20of%20100%20is%20considered%20%26quot%3Bon%20par%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20the%20number%20of%20visits%20and%20locations%20per%20chain%2C%20with%20a%20score%20greater%20than%20100%20indicating%20the%20chain%20is%20%26quot%3Bexcelling%20at%20attracting%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaising%20Cane's%20came%20second%20in%20the%20fast-casual%20sector%20with%20a%20fidelity%20score%20of%20158.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInMarket%20attributed%20Shake%20Shack's%20runaway%20Q2%20success%20to%20its%20limited-time%20menu%20offerings%20during%20tax%20season%20and%20its%20first%20loyalty%20offering%20on%20its%20app%20in%20June.%20The%20chain%20offered%20%241%20off%20soda%20and%20task-based%20offers%20to%20customers%2C%20in%20which%20they%20could%20earn%20discounts%20by%20visiting%20more%20often.%20For%20example%2C%20ordering%20two%20burgers%20on%20separate%20visits%20within%2030%20days%20granted%20%2410%20off%20the%20next%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20drive%20for%20finding%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-chains-best-value-10-dollars-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20value%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20also%20sending%20customers%20toward%20the%20fast-food%20segment.%20Also%20called%20quick-service%20restaurants%2C%20these%20establishments%20sacrifice%20some%20ambiance%20and%20customization%20options%20in%20favor%20of%20prioritizing%20speed%20and%20convenience%2C%20usually%20for%20on-the-go%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsit%20Sharma%2C%20an%20analyst%20for%20the%20Motley%20Fool%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20in%20times%20of%20economic%20uncertainty%2C%20diners%20downgrade%20the%20types%20of%20restaurants%20they%20patronize%20most%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20affluent%20spenders%20in%20the%20economy%20feel%20the%20pinch%20when%20prices%20are%20rising%2C%20and%20so%20we%20see%20a%20fun%20drop-down%20effect%20where%20those%20who%20only%20eat%20at%2C%20like%2C%20the%20best%20establishments%20will%20drop%20down%20to%20some%20chains%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20see%20those%20who%20might%20eat%20at%20higher-end%20chains%20drop%20down%20into%20the%20fast%20casual%20segment%20and%20so%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInMarket%20found%20Chick-fil-A%20had%20the%20highest%20fidelity%20score%20in%20the%20quick-service%20segment%2C%20with%20a%20score%20of%20267%2C%20after%20the%20chain%20topped%20the%20ACSI%20Customer%20Satisfaction%20Index%20for%20Quick-Service%20Restaurants%20for%20the%2011th%20year%20in%20a%20row.%20McDonald's%20followed%20with%20a%20score%20of%20164.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20firm%20found%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-new-menu-spicy-egg-mcmuffin-breakfast-taste-test-hashbrowns-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMcDonald's%20diners%3C%2Fa%3E%20tend%20to%20stick%20closely%20to%20the%20brand.%20According%20to%20InMarket%2C%20between%2039%25%20and%2044%25%20of%20diners%20at%20Chick-fil-A%2C%20Sonic%2C%20and%20Wendy's%20also%20visited%20a%20McDonald's%20during%20the%20second%20quarter.%20Conversely%2C%20a%20maximum%20of%2016%25%20of%20McDonald's%20visitors%20visited%20a%20Chick-fil-A%2C%20Sonic%2C%20or%20Wendy's%20during%20the%20same%20timeframe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiners-fast-food-vs-fast-casual-shake-shack-chickfila-loyalty-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755994810000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a90a1f194a2d49b8af1113%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdi