now%20dealing%20with%20the%20shame%20and%20embarrassment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20difficult%20to%20admit%20that%20I%20was%20scammed.%20Until%20they%20read%20it%20here%2C%20most%20of%20my%20children%20will%20have%20been%20unaware%20of%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20finally%20told%20my%20oldest%20son%2C%20he%20admitted%20he'd%20almost%20been%20a%20victim%20himself.%20He'd%20responded%20to%20a%20text%20about%20a%20package%20being%20held%20by%20the%20post%20office.%20Fortunately%20for%20him%2C%20he%20realized%20what%20was%20happening%20in%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20made%20peace%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20no%20one%20is%20going%20to%20be%20punished%20for%20scamming%20me%3B%20I'm%20just%20one%20more%20statistic.%20My%20police%20report%20is%20in%20the%20same%20black%20hole%20as%20countless%20others%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20I%20don't%20still%20feel%20the%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20every%20time%20I%20contact%20a%20customer%20service%20representative%20about%20any%20financial%20issue%2C%20my%20stomach%20clenches.%20I%20get%20a%20little%20sweaty%2C%20and%20I%20start%20to%20panic.%20I%20worry%20that%20I'll%20get%20scammed%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20reactions%20may%20actually%20be%20healthy.%20Hopefully%2C%20they'll%20protect%20me%20from%20becoming%20a%20victim%20again.%20They%20were%20there%20the%20first%20time%3B%20I%20just%20didn't%20pay%20attention.%20I'll%20be%20paying%20attention%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscammed-out-of-thousands-shame-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755951422000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a4c9ee194a2d49b8aece7e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscammed-out-of-thousands-shame-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20always%20thought%20I%20knew%20better%20than%20to%20get%20scammed%20out%2