.com%2Fblog%2Fbeyond-the-numbers-understanding-the-affordability-of-living-in-the-hamptons%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Agency%20Hamptons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20local%20real%20estate%20agency%2C%20reported%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20the%20Hamptons%20is%2047.1%25%20higher%20than%20the%20national%20average%2C%20and%20the%20average%20income%20is%20%24125%2C861.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAmber%20Waves%20also%20sold%20its%20own%20branded%20versions%20of%20dips%20and%20sauces%2C%20such%20as%20guacamole%20(%2415)%20and%20hummus%20(%2426).%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22amber%20waves%20prepared%20foods%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a4cebc194a2d49b8aecef3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20almost%20everything%20was%20Amber%20Waves-branded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20can't%20forget%20the%20prepared%20foods%2C%20either.%20These%20roasted%20veggies%20(%2415)%20and%20spicy%20sesame%20tuna%20(%2416)%20looked%20delicious.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22amber%20waves%20prepared%20foods%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a4cf0ccfc04e97619ba7f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20packages%20also%20had%20helpful%20instructions%20on%20how%20to%20cook%20the%20dishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20were%20also%20wraps%20to%20go%2C%20such%20as%20this%20%2418%20chicken%20Caesar%20wrap.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22amber%20waves%20foods%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a4cfc0cfc04e97619ba800%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221422%5C%22%3E%3Cfi