-turn-farmers-organic-farming-middlemen-profits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20grain%20quality%20suffers%2C%20and%20profits%20fall%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20little%20control%20over%20the%20process%2C%20many%20end%20up%20selling%20raw%20paddy%20at%20throwaway%20prices%2C%20sacrificing%20both%20income%20and%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20cycle%20traps%20farmers%20in%20frustration.%20Even%20when%20they%20grow%20organic%20or%20high-quality%20paddy%2C%20the%20poor%20recovery%20of%20existing%20mills%20means%20their%20effort%20does%20not%20translate%20into%20fair%20returns.%20For%20many%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20years%20of%20work%20amount%20to%20little%20more%20than%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFarmers%20take%20charge%20with%20a%20%E2%80%98bright%E2%80%99%20solution%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20this%20cycle%20needed%20innovation%20tailored%20to%20the%20realities%20of%20smallholder%20farmers.%20This%20is%20where%20%E2%80%98SEMA%20Alto%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20short%20for%20%E2%80%98Solar-powered%20Efficient%20Machinery%20for%20Agriculture%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20steps%20in.%20Founded%20in%202017%20in%20Bengaluru%20by%20co-founders%20Assad%20Jaffer%20and%20Dania%20Athar%2C%20the%20company%20was%20created%20to%20build%20clean%20energy%20and%20agri-tech%20solutions%20that%20lower%20costs%2C%20cut%20carbon%20emissions%2C%20and%20empower%20rural%20communities%20to%20keep%20more%20value%20from%20their%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20retrofitting%20bulky%20diesel%20mills%20that%20were%20never%20suited%20to%20villages%2C%20SEMA%20reimagined%20the%20process%20entirely.%20The%20result%20was%20a%20decentralised%2C%20solar-compatible%20rice%20mill%3A%20compact%2C%20modular%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F269716%2Fslug-best-electric-vehicle-battery-india-startup-royal-ev-low-costslug-best-electric-vehicle-battery-india-startup-royal-ev-low-cos