lue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192100.428_11zon-1755870673-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192100.428_11zon-1755870673-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-22T192100.428_11zon-1755870673-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-490942%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESEMA%E2%80%99s%20solution%20puts%20the%20power%20of%20rice%20milling%20back%20in%20the%20village%2C%20providing%20an%20energy-efficient%2C%20farmer-first%20machine%20that%20can%20work%20with%20small%20batches%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%20150%20units%20installed%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20SEMA%20Rice%20Mills%20supports%20farmers%20to%20package%20and%20sell%20rice%20of%20higher%20quality%20and%20at%20improved%20margins.%20For%20farmers%20like%20Gopi%2C%20this%20is%20more%20than%20just%20a%20machine.%20It%20marks%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20their%20agricultural%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20bridge%20that%20took%20innovation%20to%20the%20fields%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20SEMA%20designed%20the%20hardware%2C%20bringing%20it%20to%20scale%20required%20bridges%20beyond%20technology.%20The%20Council%20on%20Energy%2C%20Environment%20and%20Water%20(CEEW)%2C%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20this%20process%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Abhishek%20Jain%2C%20Director%20of%20Green%20Economy%20and%20Impact%20Innovations.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20its%20%E2%80%98Powering%20Livelihoods%E2%80%99%20initiative%2C%20a%20collaboration%20with%20Villgro%20(a%20social%20enterprise%20incubator)%2C%20CEEW%20helped%20unlock%